{
  "stem": "4226.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It would have been about five days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We weren't traveling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were sitting a day in Karlsfeld BMW.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then no electricity.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and then--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we were liberated, the Americans-- one American officer said, just sit quiet because behind us is the Red Cross, and the infantry unit, and the supplies.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came about-- roughly about an hour after this tank column.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What they saw-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they had the good, good shoes in the back of the tank.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just strings holding it, dangling in the-- in the air there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rubber boots, all sorts of boots they can use it in different terrain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They saw this, wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They gave it to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They undone these shoes, whoever wanted it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some fitted, some didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And rifles from German guard-- we had rifles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took it from the guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What we had rifles, the old, old rifles they had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The five-bullet rifles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If we had it, prisoners, they didn't touch it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When they found, they broke the wood part on the train's axle and they throw it on the heap.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then they took the guards in and took them prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But these, these these two guys who live in Israel, three of us, we started walking, because we saw the station about-- in-- on the horizon still, station building.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We come to the station, it says Staltach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were at Staltach, and there's no houses here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the houses were further in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We went into the village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We saw the first house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A note in German language, there's 10 prisoners living here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The next house, eight prisoners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were Yugoslav prisoners of war, not in pajamas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
